# seedPool.ts output: deployments/sepolia.json (real, live addresses) is public, non-secret
# blockchain data and is committed intentionally. Fork-run output is not a real deployment —
# each `--network sepoliaFork` run forks live state fresh and discards it on exit, so a pool
# address written there is only meaningful for the run that produced it. Never commit it.
deployments/*Fork.json

